      "duration": 2.75,
      "size": 43920,
      "text": "相传大禹治水时，一只神龟从洛水浮出，背上刻着一幅奇异的数字图案。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "magic-square",
      "section_id": "intro",
      "line_id": "intro-2",
      "filename": "intro-intro-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/magic-square/intro-intro-2.mp3",
      "duration": 1.76,
      "size": 28224,
      "text": "古人称它为洛书，也就是最早的三阶幻方。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "magic-square",
      "section_id": "build",
      "line_id": "build-1",
      "filename": "build-build-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/magic-square/build-build-1.mp3",
      "duration": 2.21,
      "size": 35424,
      "text": "奇数阶幻方有一个优雅的填法，叫暹罗法，又叫楼梯法。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "magic-square",
      "section_id": "build",
      "line_id": "build-3",
      "filename": "build-build-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/magic-square/build-build-3.mp3",
      "duration": 2.73,
      "size": 43632,
      "text": "走出边界就从对边绕回来；如果目标格已经有数，就改放到当前格的正下方。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "magic-square",
      "section_id": "verify",
      "line_id": "verify-1",
      "filename": "verify-verify-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/magic-square/verify-verify-1.mp3",
      "duration": 1.75,
      "size": 27936,
      "text": "填完之后，我们来验证：把任意一行加起来。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "magic-square",
      "section_id": "verify",
      "line_id": "verify-2",
      "filename": "verify-verify-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/magic-square/verify-verify-2.mp3",
      "duration": 2.08,
      "size": 33264,
      "text": "再把任意一列、两条对角线加起来，得数完全相同。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "magic-square",
      "section_id": "verify",
      "line_id": "verify-3",
      "filename": "verify-verify-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/magic-square/verify-verify-3.mp3",
      "duration": 1.44,
      "size": 23040,
      "text": "这个所有线共有的和，就叫做幻常数。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "magic-square",
      "section_id": "property",
      "line_id": "prop-2",
      "filename": "property-prop-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/magic-square/property-prop-2.mp3",
      "duration": 2.26,
      "size": 36144,
      "text": "三阶幻方的幻常数是十五，五阶是六十五，七阶是一百七十五。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "magic-square",
      "section_id": "interaction",
      "line_id": "int-1",
      "filename": "interaction-int-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/magic-square/interaction-int-1.mp3",
      "duration": 2.36,
      "size": 37728,
      "text": "切换三阶、五阶、七阶，看暹罗法怎样铺满整个方阵。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "magic-square",
      "section_id": "summary",
      "line_id": "sum-1",
